      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, while the M-Variable differential ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent preventive maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. Equipped with a tuned suspension featuring Bilstein B16 coilovers, it maintains exceptional lateral grip and steering feedback. A driver-focused example with a solid mechanical baseline.",
